update.clogs:
Base Version: 416.0.0.47.66
Base Updated

Added: View Blocked Profiles Secretly. (Premium)

Added: Mark as Seen after Reply (DMs) — The sender will see 'seen' only after you reply. (Premium)

Added: Private Screen Mode — Prevent people around you from seeing your screen, only you can see your content clearly. (Premium)

Added: Show Follow Indicator in User Profiles (Mutual, Following, Follower). (Premium)

Added: Disable Group Creation When Sharing — Prevents from showing the 'Create Group' option when sharing posts, reels, or messages with multiple people. (Premium)

Added: Mark as Seen (DMs) — You can manually mark a message as seen.

Added: Hide Chats — You can now hide chats.Added: Filter Feed by Following.

Added: Remove Bottom Space (Beta) — It removes bottom space from navigation bar.

Added: Add Accounts without Limits.

Fixed: Photos/Videos was not Showing in Gallery.

Fixed: Follow Indicator bugs.

Fixed: Mention Indicator bugs.

Fixed: Add to Story Crashes.

Fixed: Random Crash issues.

Fixed: Some Random UI glitches.

Improved: View Once Media Downloader in DMs — No need to enable Anti-View Once to download.

Improved: Set Story Upload Time Format.

Improved: Performance (2x faster).

Improved: Pinch-to-Zoom in View Profile Picture.

Misc: Re-arranged Filter Notifications from DMs to Long Press on Chat List.

Misc: Re-arranged View Saved Bio and Caption from Main Settings to Miscellaneous.
